          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-13">
            Porque hasta cuando te pones modo "celosita" y me miras con esa carita tan tierna, me derrites el corazón y solo me dan ganas de abrazarte fuerte.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Razón 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(251,113,133,0.15)] group">
          <h4 class="text-purple-400 font-bold text-lg mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z"/></svg>
            </div>
            Por tu fuerza
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-13">
            Admiro la forma en la que luchas por lo que quieres. Me inspiras a ser mejor persona todos los días solo con verte intentarlo.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Razón 4 -->
        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(251,191,36,0.15)] group">
          <h4 class="text-amber-400 font-bold text-lg mb-3 flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-400">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/></svg>
            </div>
            Porque eres tú
          </h4>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed pl-13">
            No necesito una razón complicada. Simplemente te quiero porque eres tú, la casualidad más hermosa y preciosa de mi vida.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ══ MODAL DE POEMAS ══ -->
  <div id="modal-poema" class="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4 opacity-0 pointer-events-none transition-all duration-300 backdrop-blur-md bg-black/70">
